downloadDescription: Presentation from the Microsoft Exchange Community (MEC) Technical Airlift - September 13-14, 2022
detailsSection:
This session covers new features and improvements we have made in Outlook calendar over the last year.

1. Compliant Meetings: Make your meetings secure and compliant by applying sensitivity labels.
2. G-Suite Migrator: Calendar migration through Google workspace migrator now supports migrating online meeting links. More enhancements planned to be released this year.
3. Shared Calendars: We made improvements to the way shared calendars in Microsoft 365 and rolled it out to delegates.

Recording of presentation by Mouli Gopalakrishnan, Harini Palaniswamy, and Kiran Rajarathna is at https://youtu.be/Bp0m1xW3F2Q.
